movies.title: The Rum Diary
movies.description: The Rum Diary is a 2011 American comedy-drama film written and directed by Bruce Robinson, based on the 1998 novel of the same name by Hunter S. Thompson.

movies.title: Free Guy
movies.description: In the extremely popular video game, Free City, a NPC named Guy learns the true nature of his existence when he meets the girl of his dreams, a human player. This player's interactions with Guy has massive affects on him, the game, and real world as they play it.

movies.title: Rise of the Legend
movies.description: RISE OF THE LEGEND is a story about Lee Chong Wei, who was born in a poor family. He has the talent of playing badminton and went through a lot of difficulties with the spirit of never giving up, finally he becomes a national player.

movies.title: Aquaman
movies.description: Arthur Curry, the human-born heir to the underwater kingdom of Atlantis, goes on a quest to prevent a war between the worlds of ocean and land.

movies.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
movies.description: Comedy series following the exploits of Det. Jake Peralta and his diverse, lovable colleagues as they police the NYPD's 99th Precinct.

movies.title: Inglourious Basterds
movies.description: In Nazi-occupied France during World War II, a plan to assassinate Nazi leaders by a group of Jewish U.S. soldiers coincides with a theatre owner's vengeful plans for the same.
